main event: A civilian in Willowick, Ohio reported seeing a single unidentified object on October 14, 1966.
interesting points: The witness reported that the object disappeared behind some houses and could not be seen through any openings.
The witness had no explanation for what they saw.
The Air Force requested the witness complete a PSTD Form 164 to provide more information for evaluation.
The Air Force thanked the witness for reporting the observation to Project Blue Book.
The Air Force concluded there was insufficient data to evaluate the sighting.
